name: The End Is Never The End
name_original: The End Is Never The End
description:
A game where anytime you die, it's a new beginning. You play as a square that is in another world and is trying to get back to it's world. 

Controls

A /D to Move

Space to Jump

Space(twice) to Double Jump

Space while on a wall to Wall Jump

Left Shift to Dash

Left Click to Change Gravity Up

Right Click to Change Gravity Down

Update Note v1.2

• Fixed the character movement 

• Improved the visuals

Have Fun!!!
